# Never commit collected host evidence.
IR-Logs-*/
**/IR-Logs-*/

# Local OS/editor noise.
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.tmp
*.bak

# Archives often contain collected evidence.
*.zip
*.7z
*.rar
*.tar
*.tar.gz
*.tgz

# Common secret-bearing local files.
.env
.env.*
id_rsa
id_ed25519
*.pem
*.key
*.pfx
*.p12
